===Noun===
'''dawn''' (''plural'' '''[[dawns]]''')

# The [[rising]] of the [[sun]].
# (uncountable) The [[time]] when the sun rises. 
#:''She rose before '''dawn''' to meet the train.''
# (uncountable) The [[beginning]].
#:''The '''dawn''' of civilisation.''
# A [[woman]]'s name.  
#:'''''Dawn''', go away I'm no good for you.'' - [[w:Frankie Valli|Frankie Valli]] from the song of the same name.
# A 1970s vocal group, usually referred to by its lead singer: ''[[w:Tony Orlando|Tony Orlando]] and '''Dawn'''.''

